<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Activate Your Picverse Account</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap');
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f8;
        }
        .email-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8d59f3 0%, #6c41d4 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8d59f3 0%, #6c41d4 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(108, 65, 212, 0.3);
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #8d59f3;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .activation-link {
            word-break: break-all;
            color: #8d59f3;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            border: 1px dashed #8d59f3;
        }
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                width: 100%;
                margin: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">✅</div>
            <h1>Picverse</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Activate Your Account</h2>
            <p>Welcome to Picverse! We're excited to have you join our creative community.</p>
            <p>To complete your registration and start exploring amazing content, please click the button below to activate your account:</p>
            <a href="{{activateUrl}}" class="button">Activate Account</a>
            <p>Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
            <div class="activation-link">{{activateUrl}}</div>
            <p>This activation link will expire in 24 hours for security reasons. If you didn't create an account, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© 2024 Picverse. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>If you didn't create an account, please <a href="#">contact our support team</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>